data.description: Discover peace, privacy, and comfort in this 1760 sq ft home on 2.5 acres. 2 bedrooms + 2 bonus rooms, 2 spacious living areas, and a private ensuite primary bedroom. Ample space for development and a dream shop, plus easy access to Bandix Dog Park and HWY 16. Centrally located between Gig Harbor and Port Orchard for an easy commute.  Country living with all the local amenities close by. VA assumable rate of 5.75% with approval.
